  <LINE>FIRE DEPARTMENT.</LINE>
  <LINE>FOB INSURING PROPERTY AGAINST LOSS OR DAMAGE BY FIRE.</LINE>
  <LINE>Property of almost every description may be secured</LINE>
  <LINE>against accidents arising from Fire, by the Payment of</LINE>
  <LINE>a small Annual Premium ; and Risks involving more than</LINE>
  <LINE>ordinary hazard are moderately rated.</LINE>
  <LINE>All Losses, when satisfactorily ascertained, are imme-</LINE>
  <LINE>diately paid; and the Directors of this Incorporation</LINE>
  <LINE>confidently refer to the liberality and promptitude which</LINE>
  <LINE>have hitherto marked their settlement of claims.</LINE>
