  <LINE>NON-PARTICIPATING POLICIES.</LINE>
  <LINE>The Low Rates charged in the Non-Participating Class</LINE>
  <LINE>are peculiarly well adapted for Loan Transactions ; also,</LINE>
  <LINE>where the object is to assure a specific Sum payable at</LINE>
  <LINE>death, at the lowest rate of Premium compatible with</LINE>
  <LINE>Security.</LINE>
